    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car featuring the legendary S54 straight-six engine with individual throttle bodies. It has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a complete VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The chassis is reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points to ensure structural integrity under load. Power is managed by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential, providing tactile feedback and precise power delivery. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with its age, the suspension has been refreshed with Bilstein dampers for optimized turn-in and damping. This is a high-performance machine sorted for the twisties, not a garage queen.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
