    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a meticulously maintained E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This chassis has been technically sorted with a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common floor pan fatigue and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul for optimal cam timing. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring exceptional traction and corner-exit rotation. The suspension maintains its factory-intended kinematics, providing the communicative steering and balanced damping characteristic of this legendary platform. A true driver\u2019s specimen that balances mechanical purity with visceral performance.",
